about it and now they exploded.

364
00:34:33,760 --> 00:34:37,860
That's no news
to their close associates.

365
00:34:38,760 --> 00:34:45,760
Ha. She always talked
as if she were some elegant lady.

366
00:34:45,760 --> 00:34:50,960
