dedicated to his love, Clara.

427
00:40:06,760 --> 00:40:07,900
Ms. Uhm.

428
00:40:07,900 --> 00:40:10,760
Don't try to deceive me anymore.

429
00:40:10,760 --> 00:40:13,760
You love me too.

430
00:40:13,760 --> 00:40:15,830
