to that old gigolo.

467
00:42:37,330 --> 00:42:39,760
Watch your mouth. Old gigolo?

468
00:42:39,760 --> 00:42:42,760
Stop beating my husband.

469
00:42:42,760 --> 00:42:44,800
She's really crazy.

470
00:42:47,760 --> 00:42:49,760
