497
00:44:33,200 --> 00:44:36,400
I'm coming back
from a business trip.

498
00:44:36,400 --> 00:44:38,760
Let's have dinner together.

499
00:44:38,760 --> 00:44:40,760
Okay.

500
00:44:53,300 --> 00:44:55,760
